name: tRNA (guanine46-N7)-methyltransferase
reaction: S-adenosyl-L-methionine + guanine46 in tRNA = S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + N7-methylguanine46 in tRNA [RN:R00600]
comment: The enzyme specifically methylates guanine46 at N7 in tRNA.
